            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "I’ve been tinkering with a VSCode extension called Paper. The main motivation behind Paper is to create a place to keep the things (files, folders, location within a file) I often go back to when working on a feature or fixing a bug.\n\n"
              },
              {
                "type": "link",
                "url": "https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=Raathigeshan.paper"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "\n\nI’ve been using it for a while and I find it really useful. If you have ideas or feedback feel free to share "
              },
              {
                "type": "emoji",
                "name": "slightly_smiling_face"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
