  {
    "client_msg_id": "0b6c6391-4b0f-4fcf-b668-b18dee8f46e5",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "I wanted the document to be a place where I can keep multiple things on related to a feature I’m working on. Currently the document supports a file bookmark or a bookmark to a selection in a file. Also it supports a tree view to show directories.\n\nA document means I can add a bookmark and elaborate on it using text. It feels a bit more flexible.\n\nI’m hoping to make the editor support more interactive views. For example a widget that shows file navigation history might be useful.\n\nThe document mostly acts like a flexible canvas to place these things on.",
    "user": "US6TKS2HW",
    "ts": "1630279208.009800",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
